Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
report_cell_stack_group(25.10)                  report_cell_stack_group(25.10)

Name
       report_cell_stack_group - Reports the cell stack group definition

Syntax
       report_cell_stack_group

       [-help]

       [-file <string>]

       [-name <string>]

       Reports the cell stack group definition.

Parameters
       -file <file_name>
              Specifies  the  file  name  in which the reported information is
              saved.

              By  default,  all  cell  stack  groups  are  reported   to   the
              cell_stack_group.rpt file.

       -help  Outputs  a  brief description that includes type and default in-
              formation for each report_cell_stack_group parameter.

              For a detailed description of the command and all of its parame-
              ters, use the man command: man report_cell_stack_group

       -name <group_name>
              Specifies the group(s) that needs to be reported.

Related Information
              * specify_cell_stack_group

              * delete_cell_stack_group

